name: Verify new customer can be created

testSteps.description: Example #1: {username=mngr201145, userpass=urEpUta, customername=Loc Nguyen, gender=male, dateofbrith=01-23-1983, address=Nguyen Van Dau Binh Thanh, city=HCM, state=VN, pinno=123456, phone=0909999999, email=@aaa.com, password=12345678}

children.description: Given User login to Guru99 Bank with "mngr201145" and "urEpUta"
When Title of login page is Guru99 Bank Manager Homepage displays "mngr201145"
Then Click to New Customer on the left menu
Then Enter valid values to all field to add a New Customer "Loc Nguyen", "male", "01-23-1983", "Nguyen Van Dau Binh Thanh", "HCM", "VN", "123456", "0909999999", "@aaa.com", "12345678"
Then See the Customer Registered Successfully message
Then Verify the correctness of Customer Registered "Loc Nguyen", "male", "01-23-1983", "Nguyen Van Dau Binh Thanh", "HCM", "VN", "123456", "0909999999", "@aaa.com", "12345678"
